Articles.Content:
When I try to load KSP in, it just decides not to load in fully after a bit of loading. I tried to uninstall and reinstall the game but it did not work.

Here's my latest crash log

https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/0BzwjJRrDQO8DV0dUcnoxWThVOTA?usp=sharing

You appear to be using mods, please try removing the mods and see if the issue persists, if it does please reply.

If it does not, I would suggest you add the mods one at a time to find the offending mod (probably something just not updated to 1.3) and post in the modded installs subforum.

Hope this helps
Could be crashing due to going over the RAM limit. Happens to me when I install new new textures and ATM tries to compress them. Or you have an unused network adapter, like hamachi or tunngle.
